- **‚úÖ Backend Period Logic**: Enhanced `getStats` tRPC procedure to accept `comparisonType` parameter and calculate comparison periods correctly
- **‚úÖ Previous Period Calculation**: Implemented same-length previous period calculation (e.g., if viewing Feb 1-28, compares to 28 days in January)
- **‚úÖ Year-over-Year Comparison**: Added YoY comparison option (e.g., Feb 2025 vs Feb 2024)
- **‚úÖ Dynamic Descriptions**: KPI card descriptions now dynamically show "vs. previous period" or "vs. same period last year"
