### **3. Date Range Integration ‚úÖ**
- **‚úÖ Comparison Type Toggle**: Period comparison toggle now properly affects all KPI calculations
- **‚úÖ Date Range Dependency**: All stats queries now respect both date range and comparison type selections
- **‚úÖ Smart Period Logic**: Backend automatically calculates appropriate comparison periods based on user selections
